dosageInstruction.text:
12 g (3 tablet), ORAL, EVERY 15 MINUTES IF NEEDED, Starting on Sun xx/xx/xxxx at 1315, Until Wed xx/xx/xxxx at 1152, hypoglycemia
Give 3 tabs for blood glucose levels 60-70 mg/dL. Give 6 tabs for blood glucose levels less than 60 mg/dL.

1,000 mg, ORAL, TWO TIMES DAILY WITH MEALS, First dose on Wed xx/xx/xxxx at 1700, Until Discontinued
Administer with food to minimize GI upset.
